        options: ["Start high-intensity statin immediately","Start moderate-intensity statin based on the borderline risk category","Defer statin therapy -- a CAC score of 0 indicates very low near-term risk; recommend lifestyle optimization and reassess in 5-10 years","PCSK9 inhibitor is the most appropriate first-line therapy"],
